               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430227-name-1262" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1262" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1262" type="surname" value="CATTELL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1262" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN CATTELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Robert George Cattell, tobacco<lb></lb>nist, Goswell-street. On the 1st of March I missed a bundle of about 100 cigars from a board in the shop window—I had seen them safe about an hour and a half before—the prisoner was brought into my shop—I had seen him in my shop on the Monday before—the cigars have not been found.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430227-name-1263" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1263" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1263" type="surname" value="POOL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1263" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD POOL</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Whitecross-street. Between one and two o'clock on the 1st of March, I saw the prisoner come out of Mr. Cattell's shop with a bundle of cigars in his hand—he threw them into another boy's apron and they ran away—I am quite sure the prisoner is the boy who came out with the cigars in his hand—I ran to my master's door, and then I ran after the prisoner—I called, "Stop thief"—he turned round, swore at me, and asked what I wanted—I stuck to him—he tried to get away, and struck me—I fell down, and a gentleman took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> He came hallooing out "Stop thief"—I turned and said "What do you want?"—he said, "I will tell you what I want," and then he struck me, and I hit him again. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I did not hit him, he hit me.</p>
